---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>白中宝 | Baizhongbao</h1>
			<p>
				欢迎来到我的个人博客。这里记录我在技术领域的探索、学习笔记和项目实践。
			</p>
			<p>
				A personal blog where I share my tech journey, learning notes, and project work.
			</p>
			<p>
				目前主要关注的方向 / Current focus areas:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>深度学习与预测性维护 / Deep Learning & Predictive Maintenance</li>
				<li>LLM 应用开发 / LLM Application Development</li>
				<li>Web 开发 / Web Development</li>
				<li>自动化工具 / Automation Tools</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				欢迎浏览 <a href="/blog">博客</a> 查看更多内容，或访问 <a href="/about">关于我</a> 了解更多信息。
			</p>
			<p>
				Feel free to explore the <a href="/blog">blog</a> or visit <a href="/about">about</a> to learn more.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
